casebody.data:
Andrew S. MUELLER
v.
Denise D. MUELLER and
Denise D. Mueller
v.
Eric Kee. No. 675P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 2, 2006. Timothy M. Stokes, Charlotte, for Eric Kee. Timothy H. Graham, Charlotte, for Andrew S. Mueller.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 7th day of December 2005 by Defendant (Eric Kee) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31 (Petition for Writ of Certiorari), the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 2nd day of March 2006."
